\[
\sum_{k=1}^{3n}m^{*}(q_{k}+E)=\sum_{k=1}^{3n}m^{*}(E)>\sum_{k=1}^{3n}\frac{1}{n}=3
\]

\end_inset

若 
\begin_inset Formula $m^{*}$
\end_inset

 具备有限可加性，则将有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathopen{m^{*}}\left(\bigcup_{k=1}^{3n}(q_{k}+E)\right)=\sum_{k=1}^{3n}m^{*}(q_{k}+E)>3
\]

\end_inset

这与由“单调性”导出的
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bigcup_{k=1}^{3n}(q_{k}+E)\subset X\implies\mathopen{m^{*}}\left(\bigcup_{k=1}^{3n}(q_{k}+E)\right)\le m^{*}(X)\le3
\]

\end_inset

矛盾。
\end_layout

