若 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 的子集 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\forall A\subset\mathbb{R}^{n}\right)\left(m^{*}(A)=m^{*}(A\cap E)+m^{*}(A\setminus E)\right)
\]

\end_inset

则称 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 是一个 (Lebesgue) 
\bar under
